# Local secrets and broker/API credentials - mirrors .gitignore's own list.
# lean.json is tracked in git (its ib-account/ib-user-name/ib-password/
# ib-trading-mode fields ship as empty placeholders, hand-filled locally per
# development/infrastructure.md's V2-22 runbook) so it must be excluded here
# too, or a locally-populated copy gets baked straight into the image layer
# on the next `aq docker build` - and that image is the same one published
# to ghcr (single fat target, no slim variant).
.env
.env.*
!.env.compose.example
!.env.live.example
ib_config.py
*_config.local.py
config.local.json
lean.local.json
lean.json
*.key
*.pem
